702
00:49:15.525 --> 00:49:18.445
I was with my best friend Kathy, and we stood in disbelief.

703
00:49:19.305 --> 00:49:23.685
We were 12. There were no cell phones, no advance warning.

704
00:49:24.425 --> 00:49:27.005
We arrived to a burning building and fire trucks.

705
00:49:27.425 --> 00:49:28.765
It is a vivid image.

706
00:49:29.855 --> 00:49:32.085
Since then, I've thought about those boys

707
00:49:32.785 --> 00:49:35.125
and wondered about their lives and what went wrong.

708
00:49:35.755 --> 00:49:37.725
They were not traditional students,

709
00:49:39.225 --> 00:49:41.805
but they were clever with their hands, able

710
00:49:41.805 --> 00:49:43.485
to fix things and build things.

711
00:49:44.265 --> 00:49:46.685
But schools didn't consider that valuable.

712
00:49:47.745 --> 00:49:49.645
Didn't consider them valuable.

713
00:49:50.475 --> 00:49:53.205
They were ridiculed and teased and no one listened to them.

714
00:49:54.055 --> 00:49:56.765
Today we have a variety of teaching methods

715
00:49:57.265 --> 00:50:00.525
to meet the needs of all students, social workers

716
00:50:00.625 --> 00:50:02.245
and guidance counselors who listen

717
00:50:02.945 --> 00:50:04.565
and staff who understand

718
00:50:04.675 --> 00:50:07.005
that there are many different kinds of learners.

719
00:50:07.775 --> 00:50:10.045
Thankfully, some things have changed.

720
00:50:11.445 --> 00:50:15.005
I listened to my friends today giving their message in many

721
00:50:15.365 --> 00:50:18.325
languages and I thought about how life is different

722
00:50:18.325 --> 00:50:21.285
for them, how it has changed,

723
00:50:22.425 --> 00:50:26.445
how there are things they miss, things they left behind,

724
00:50:27.105 --> 00:50:28.725
and the importance of their message.

725
00:50:29.555 --> 00:50:34.325
Most left family familiar surroundings, language

726
00:50:34.345 --> 00:50:38.525
that's easy to use so much, mostly

727
00:50:38.525 --> 00:50:41.325
because of persecution, war,

728
00:50:42.265 --> 00:50:45.085
