00:50:55.465 --> 00:50:57.495
About two years ago I posted online

733
00:50:57.885 --> 00:50:59.815
that I wondered if there was anyone out there

734
00:51:00.355 --> 00:51:03.215
who I could hire to finish the edges of some granite.

735
00:51:03.295 --> 00:51:08.255
I had a reply came through. I can do it. Do you remember me?

736
00:51:09.275 --> 00:51:10.375
It was Russell Leo.

737
00:51:11.255 --> 00:51:13.335
I had him in school when he was seven years old.

738
00:51:13.995 --> 00:51:16.415
He now lived around the corner, had kids

739
00:51:16.415 --> 00:51:18.175
