740
00:51:19.035 --> 00:51:20.735
It was a delight to reconnect.

741
00:51:21.785 --> 00:51:25.155
Rick Rodriguez answered a post that I had trying

742
00:51:25.155 --> 00:51:26.715
to sell some horseshoe rings.

743
00:51:26.885 --> 00:51:31.315
