750
00:51:51.635 --> 00:51:54.955
I thought of you. You changed my way of thinking.

751
00:51:55.635 --> 00:51:57.555
I don't take things so personally anymore,

752
00:51:58.015 --> 00:52:00.675
and I'm more confident in my own self.

753
00:52:03.225 --> 00:52:05.315
Some things change whether we're ready or not.

754
00:52:05.695 --> 00:52:09.155
People grow up, we age and the world changes.

755
00:52:11.245 --> 00:52:14.165
